t">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DTownship=
_(United_States)&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D5" title=3D"Edit section: =
Usage by state"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket"=
>]</span></span></div>
